title: Chronicle of the Fourth Crusade by Geoffrey de Villehardouin
description:
Memoirs or Chronicle of the Fourth Crusade and the Conquest of Constantinople - Geoffrey de Villehardouin [epub]

Geoffrey de Villehardouin (1160-1212 AD), was an actual participant in the Fourth Crusade. Geoffry was a soldier, a Christian Knight, and one of the special envoys sent to facilitate transport of the expedition. This is his personal account of the Crusade. A true classic of great historic significance, providing rare insight to the courage and faith of these mighty Christian knights. Geoffry would go on to become one of the most distinguished historians of the period
